<varlistentry id="options.MiniPixmap">
<term>MiniPixmap  <emphasis remap='I'>pixmap</emphasis></term>
 	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies a given pixmap to display to the left of the menu item which invokes this menu, or in the title of this menu. Default pixmap size is 24x24 pixels; this size can be adjusted in Look via MiniPixmapSize.</para>
		<para>See Also: MinipixmapSize, LargeMiniPixmap, SmallMiniPixmap, MenuMiniPixmaps.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
